td.div: English: Coat of arms of the National University of Colombia, designed in 1937 upon request of the former general secretary Otto de Greiff and reedited in 1947 by the Master Francisco Duarte.
Español: Escudo de la Universidad Nacional de Colombia, diseñado en 1937 por solicitud del entonces secretario general Otto de Greiff y revisado en 1947 por el Maestro Francisco Duarte.

table.style: width:100%; clear:both; margin:0.5em auto; background-color:#f7f8ff; border:2px solid #8888aa;

tr.td: This image shows a flag, a coat of arms, a seal or some other official insignia. The use of such symbols is restricted in many countries. These restrictions are independent of the copyright status.

td.a: Redrawn coat of arms, effective 4 March 2016
